{"tid":1374490,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"［全民裝備運動］推到全港一齊做","createTime":"2019-07-27T19:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T09:39:43.000Z","uid":81586,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4e85e03032164c88e61fbac4b47d9deb86fefcbd","tid":1374490,"uid":81586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:04:58.000Z","msg":"運動目的：鑑於過往兩個月暴徒橫行，警黑勾結，市民應在日常生活起步加強個人防護意識。<br />\n<br />\n運動內容：全部人出街返工不論任何時間都隨時戴住裝備出街，等我地將抗爭日常化。<br />\n<br />\n最輕便：安全帽+口罩<br />\n中級：頭盔+護甲<br />\n最高級：頭盔+護甲+豬咀（<strong>不連漏芯</strong>）+護盾<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">元朗國國民暫時不納入為於此運動推廣名單內，如有需要可以向十八鄉委員會申請</span>"},{"pid":"92b69af5daf6ea404ad7736b4e57e02203b41e88","tid":1374490,"uid":81586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b597d60a2d544e8b13da94ac8662ed6f5cd447","tid":1374490,"uid":81586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e511f545d165dae0905c3300357d57cb75257a","tid":1374490,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:12:48.000Z","msg":"易入口少少，掛頂帽係背狼出面/皮帶度都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36a9b19d265f5ecb66aeda8b9724f2882738aef","tid":1374490,"uid":81586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93e511f545d165dae0905c3300357d57cb75257a","tid":1374490,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:12:48.000Z","msg":"易入口少少，掛頂帽係背狼出面/皮帶度都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:31:05.000Z","msg":"對付白衫暴徒可能有用"},{"pid":"752e9d875e4f2c3276c052d4bce8b53115ee1439","tid":1374490,"uid":81586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/